lead_paragraph: The U.S. Federal Bureau of Investigation gave Brazil the tip that led to arrests this week of 11 suspected militants who had discussed a possible attack on the upcoming Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, according to a Brazilian prosecutor.

headline.print_headline: FBI Led Brazil to Suspected Militants Mulling Olympic Attack: Prosecutor
